description: Alice frost is not a push over by any sense of the term. She's strong and determined. After an embarrassing season 10, Alice made a point to get some training. She was tired of getting her asshole fingered during wrestling matches. She comes back to us in season 11, bigger and stronger than ever. Her whole demeanor has changed. She's ready to finally win a match. The only problem is, Today she meets Lea Lexis ( The Romanian Rager) Lea is dominatrix and her pride will not allow her to lose today. She lost last season to Bella Wilde and for the first time ever, got fucked on the US mats. She didn't like that at all. Today, she doesn't let Alice's size intimidate her. She comes on strong and give Alice what she deserves.
title: The Romanian Rager is Back and Stronger than ever
